50|$|On {{reaching}} home, {{his enthusiasm}} is dashed {{along with the}} can of condensed milk <b>his</b> <b>companion</b> throws on the floor when <b>his</b> <b>companion</b> discovers she would have no saki but milk for the evening. <b>His</b> <b>companion</b> grows violent and bruises his eye. The next evening, on his return, he enthusiastically brings home a bottle of saki, but his home is silent. <b>His</b> <b>companion</b> had decided to leave him and had left baby Mei with a neighbour.|$|R
