60|$|Ulf {{found no}} {{difficulty}} in mounting to the top, {{although he was}} much longer than <b>his</b> <b>companion</b> in getting up. There were several sail following them, and Ulf {{was surprised at the}} knowledge <b>his</b> <b>companion</b> showed of vessels that appeared to him almost precisely similar.|$|R
